			<abstract label="Abstract:">Letters and ledgers from various members of the Merritt family.</abstract>
			<langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English</language></langmaterial>
		</did>
		<scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
			<head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
			<p>Letters from various members of the Merritt family, describing life along the Saint
				Lawrence River and in Saint Lawrence County and their pioneering travel west to
				Iowa, Wisconsin, Kansas, and Nebraska; much local color. Also several financial ledgers, account and day books, and some various publications.</p>
		</scopecontent>
